)]]\n| 1\n|-\n|align=left| [[Revolutionary Socialist Party (India)|Revolutionary Socialist Party]]\n| 1\n|-\n|align=left| [[Viduthalai Chiruthaigal Katchi]]\n| 1\n|-\n|align=left| [[All India United Democratic Front]]\n| 1\n|-\n|align=left| [[Independent politician|Independent]]\n| 1\n|-\n| rowspan=\"15\" style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\" |'''Others'''<br />Seats: '''114'''\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[YSR Congress Party]]\n| 22\n|-\n|align=left| [[All India Trinamool Congress]]\n| 22\n|-\n|align=left| [[Shiv Sena]]\n| 18\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Biju Janata Dal]]\n| 12\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Bahujan Samaj Party]]\n| 10\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Telangana Rashtra Samithi]]\n| 9\n|-\n| align=\"left\" |[[Samajwadi Party]]\n| 5\n|-\n|align=left| [[Telugu Desam Party]]\n| 3\n|-\n|align=left| [[Communist Party of India (Marxist)]]\n| 3\n|-\n|align=left| [[Communist Party of India]]\n| 2\n|-\n|align=left| [[All India Majlis-e-Ittehadul Muslimeen]]\n| 2\n|-\n|align=left| [[Janata Dal (Secular)]]\n| 1\n|-\n|align=left| [[Aam Aadmi Party]]\n| 1\n|-\n|align=left| [[Independent politician|Independent]]\n| 2\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| Vacant\n| 1\n|-\n|colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| '''Total'''\n| '''543'''\n|}\n\n== See also ==\n*[[List of constituencies of the Lok Sabha]]\n*[[Parliament of India]]\n*[[Rajya Sabha]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|Lok Sabha}}\n* [http://loksabha.nic.in/ Lok Sabha website]\n* [https://resultuniversity.com/loksabha-election 1951 to 2014 Lok Sabha Election Results in Detail]\n* [https://eci.gov.in/general-election/general-elections-2019/ General Elections 2019]\n* [http://www.loksabhaelections.in/ Lok Sabha General Election 2019 - Parliamentary Polls 2019 Latest News & Updates]\n\n{{Lok Sabha}}\n{{Parliament of India}}\n{{Government of India}}\n{{Legislatures of India}}\n{{National lower houses}}\n\n[[Category:Lok Sabha| ]]\n