.org/ Official website]\n{{FM station data|KOHS}}\n*{{FCC letter|letterid=69343|callsign=KOHS|hcards=yes}}\n\n{{Salt Lake City Radio}}\n\n[[Category:Radio stations in Utah|OHS]]\n[[Category:High school radio stations in the United States]]\n[[Category:Radio stations established in 1974]]\n[[Category:Utah County, Utah]]\n\n\n{{Utah-radio-station-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Stereorock", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/KOHS"}
